<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/17 (Thu.) The Year That Was &amp; The Year That Will Be / Is Watching the News Bad for Mental Health? (Host: Michael)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=507&amp;p=529#p529"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Place:</span> Zoom Meeting<br /><span style="color: #FF0000">Agenda:</span><br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br /><br />Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">會議 ID:</span>929 8726 6213<br /><span style="color: #FF0000">密碼:</span>112233<br /><br /><br />Session 1: The Year That Was &amp; The Year That Will Be<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://blog.zoom.us/the-year-that-was-the-year-that-will-be/">https://blog.zoom.us/the-year-that-was- ... t-will-be/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you think the world has been changing dramatically after COVID-19 pandemic happened?<br />What are temporary changes and what are permanent?<br />2.Does COVID-19 cause your personal reset on how you think about your lives, what’s important to you, what your priorities are?<br />3.Have you ever tried any type of delivery (like UberEats or Foodpanda) for grocery or restaurant meals during the pandemic? Why or why not?<br />4.Share your and your family members' life and work changes after government announced level 3 of COVID-19 alert.<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 2: Is Watching the News Bad for Mental Health?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.verywellmind.com/is-watching-the-news-bad-for-mental-health-4802320">https://www.verywellmind.com/is-watchin ... th-4802320</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you agree that watching the news is bad for mental health? Why or why not?<br />2.During the pandemic, do you feel a little stress changing in your sleep or eating patterns, worrying about your health and the health of loved ones, and difficulty concentrating?<br />3.How do you manage your news consumption?<br />4.How can you validate the news is from reliable outlets, can you decipher fake news?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Fri Jun 11, 2021 9:36 pm</p><hr />
